    <topic parent="VideoPlayer Control Events" parentType="guide" elementName="onLoaded">VideoPlayer onLoaded Event</topic>
    <description>Fires after when a new video has been loaded into the VideoPlayer control.</description>
    <discussion>
        <p>The *[ui:onLoaded]* event is triggered when a video has been loaded into the Video Player. The event is passed one argument:</p>
        <p>
            <list>
                <item>
                    <name-title>Argument</name-title>
                    <description-title>Description</description-title>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <name>*[js:duration]*</name>
                    <description>The length of the video in seconds.</description>
                </item>
            </list>
        </p>
    </discussion>
    <see>
        <ref link="ux%20data%20controls%20more%20controls%20videoplayer%20controls">VideoPlayer Control</ref>
    </see>
</page>